ns-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#333333"><br></font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial, sans-serif;"><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#333333">This is a chance to work on an intense, exciting youth programme inspiring teams of young people. There is a range of summer roles available, both for paid staff and volunteers, from between&nbsp;two and fourteen weeks, between June and September.</font></span></p><p style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#333333"><br></font></span></p><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#333333">If you think that might be of interest at all, you can get more information about the opportunities and apply at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs" target="_blank">www.ncsthechallenge.org/jobs</a>.</font></span></div></div></div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font color="#333333"><br clear="none" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;">Best wishes,&nbsp;</span><br clear="none" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;"><br>Staffing Team<br clear="none" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 18px;">NCS with The Challenge</span><br></font></span>]]></td>
